{
  "chapter": 65,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十五回「神出鬼没」。小鱼儿为探查神秘人物身份，扮成茶房潜入其房间，发现屋内一尘不染且弥漫奇异香气。铜先生突然现身，身法诡异如影随形，揭露自己早知小鱼儿身份。铜先生承诺永不杀小鱼儿，却因小鱼儿赞美母亲而勃然大怒，痛斥其母为世上最丑恶的女人。小鱼儿为维护母亲与铜先生激烈对抗，被打得满嘴流血仍不屈服。\n\n铜先生将昏迷的小鱼儿扔到花无缺面前，命其立即动手杀人。花无缺虽知师命难违，却以三月之约为由拒绝，坦言无法对毫无反抗之力的小鱼儿下手。铜先生怒斥花无缺，暗示其对小鱼儿产生异样情感。花无缺内心挣扎，感受到与小鱼儿之间某种奇妙的联系。小鱼儿被救醒后，以言语挑衅铜先生，揭露其不敢亲自动手的软肋，铜先生长啸掠下，局面紧张。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "客官可要加些茶水么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "壶里不知还有茶没有，我不如先给斟上吧，也免得客人回来没水喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么爱干净的人，倒也少见得很……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你是谁？来干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "小的是来瞧瞧，客官是不是要添些茶水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你是这店里的伙计？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "白天来的，好像不是你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "钱老大当日班，小的王三是值夜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "江小鱼果然是随机应变，对答如流。只可惜你出娘胎，我就认得你，你在我面前装什么都没有用的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你瞧不见我的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你若不愿被我瞧见，为何要来呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你想不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我想，你总不会要杀死我吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怎知我不杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "一个马上要死的人，就算瞧见你的真面目，也没什么关系，所以你若要杀我，就不妨让我瞧瞧了，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你原来就是铜先生！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那日黑蜘蛛说你武功如何如何之高，我还有些不信，今日一见，才知道他不是吹牛的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你用不着奉承我，我既不想杀你，就永远不会杀你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "永远不会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我见了你这样爱干净，又弄出这香气，本来以为你是个女人的……幸好你不是女人，否则你就算说不杀我，我也不相信。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不相信女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "妇人之言，绝不可听，谁若相信女人，谁就倒霉了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你母亲难道不是女人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "天下的女人，有谁能和我母亲相比，她又温柔、又美丽……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "世上别的女人，若和我母亲相比，简直连粪土也不如，我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你……你说过永远不杀我的，说出来的话怎能不算。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因你满嘴胡说八道，令人可恨。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我几时胡说八道了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你母亲是好是坏，是美是丑，你根本未见过，如此为她吹嘘，不是胡说八道是什么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你……你怎知我未见过我母亲的面？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我不知道谁知道。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我母亲长得是何模样？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你母亲跛脚驼背，又麻又秃，乃是世上最丑最恶的女人，世上无论哪一个女人都比她好看得多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "放屁放屁，你才是胡说八道！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你再敢骂，我就杀了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "只要你承认我母亲是最温柔、最美丽的，我就不骂你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你死也不肯承认你母亲是最丑最恶的女人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你情愿为她死？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我母亲究竟与你有什么仇恨，你要如此骂她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还不承认？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你有本事，就宰了我吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "莫非是铜……铜先生？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "出来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "移花宫门下，怎地也贪酒贪睡起来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你自然已知道我是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "晚辈出宫时，家师已吩咐过，只要见到先生，便如见家师，先生所有指示，晚辈无不遵命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你出宫时，宫主还曾吩咐了你什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "家师要我亲手杀死一个叫江小鱼的人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "很好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你在树下站着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "接稳了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他是否江小鱼？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你杀了他吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你若不愿杀一个没有反抗之力的人，不妨先解开他的穴道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "是你救了我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我早就知道你会来救我的，我们是朋友。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，你为什么还不动手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道你不敢违抗他的话……好，你动手吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我现在不能杀你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你忘了你师父的话么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我已和他订了三个月之约，未到约期，绝不能杀他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你的师父若是知道这事，又当如何？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "师命虽不可违，但诺言也不可毁，纵然家师此刻便在这里，也不可能令晚辈做食言背信的人！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺你莫忘记，见我如见师，你敢不听我的话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "先生无论吩咐什么，弟子无不照办，只有此事，却万万不能从命。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你不杀他，只怕并非为了要守诺言，只怕还另有原囚？是么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，莫要再等三个月了！现在就动手吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "为什么不能再等三个月？你怕三个月后，他更不会动手了吗？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我怕什么！你两人是天生的冤家对头，你们的命中已注定，必有一个人要死在另一人的手上！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "既然如此，你现在为何还要逼他？你若想我现在就死，就自己动手吧……你自己为何不敢动手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 65,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    }
